Entries.default: "Hey, looks like the Here missed us."
"Stay together. Who knows what may come of this."
"Everything seems as peaceful and orderly as we left it."
"Just for once I hope this has nothing to do with us."
"Dang, Watcher! It's like the island's got up and started walking!"
"Did restoring the flow of souls result in some manner of essence feedback?"
"This is still better than the Beyond."
"It seems we did not leave all of our troubles in the Beyond."
"The Crucible shouldn't be like this! Something's wrong!"
"Oi, cap! There be three kraken worth of hungry nearby!"
